</tr></table>
<span id="Compiling-and-installing-Emacs-1"></span><h1 class="chapter">7 Compiling and installing Emacs</h1>
<span id="index-Compiling-and-installing-Emacs"></span>

<table class="menu" border="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr><td align="left" valign="top"><a href="#Installing-Emacs">7.1 How do I install Emacs?</a></td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">
</td></tr>
<tr><td align="left" valign="top"><a href="#Problems-building-Emacs">7.2 What should I do if I have trouble building Emacs?</a></td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">
</td></tr>
</table>

<hr>
<div class="section" id="Installing-Emacs">
<table class="header" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" border="0">
