<span id="Where-can-I-get-other-up_002dto_002ddate-GNU-stuff_003f"></span><h2 class="section">8.5 Where can I get other up-to-date GNU stuff?</h2>
<span id="index-Current-GNU-distributions"></span>
<span id="index-Sources-for-current-GNU-distributions"></span>
<span id="index-Stuff_002c-current-GNU"></span>
