<span id="Key-bindings-1"></span><h1 class="chapter">9 Key bindings</h1>
<span id="index-Key-bindings"></span>

<table class="menu" border="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr><td align="left" valign="top"><a href="#Binding-keys-to-commands">9.1 How do I bind keys (including function keys) to commands?</a></td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">
</td></tr>
<tr><td align="left" valign="top"><a href="#Invalid-prefix-characters">9.2 Why does Emacs say &lsquo;<samp>Key sequence XXX uses invalid prefix characters</samp>&rsquo;?</a></td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">
</td></tr>
<tr><td align="left" valign="top"><a href="#Terminal-setup-code-works-after-Emacs-has-begun">9.3 Why doesn&rsquo;t this [terminal or window-system setup] code work in my <samp>.emacs</samp> file, but it works just fine after Emacs starts up?</a></td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">
</td></tr>
<tr><td align="left" valign="top"><a href="#Working-with-function-and-arrow-keys">9.4 How do I tell what characters or symbols my function or arrow keys emit?</a></td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">
</td></tr>
<tr><td align="left" valign="top"><a href="#X-key-translations-for-Emacs">9.5 How do I set the X key &ldquo;translations&rdquo; for Emacs?</a></td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">
</td></tr>
<tr><td align="left" valign="top"><a href="#Backspace-invokes-help">9.6 Why does the <tt class="key">Backspace</tt> key invoke help?</a></td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">
</td></tr>
